According to Ukrainian e-commerce website KTC, the upcoming iPhone 13 and iPhone 13 mini will be available in a pink color and 64GB and 128GB storage configurations. The iPhone 13 Pro and iPhone 13 Pro Max would be available in new black and bronze colors in 128GB, 256GB, and 512GB storage configurations.
